            <h2>Testing of high THC NZ grown outdoor strains for Medical use</h2>
            <hr>
            <h3 style="color:#538b01;">Overview</h3>

            
            <p> 

            An associate of mine who is heavily involved in the clandestine breeding of new Medical Marijuana strains for the NZ climate wishes to conduct an underground trial of his products.
            </p>
            <p>
            He is willing to make top grade marijuana available in small quantities for <em style="color:#ff01f0; font-weight:bold; text-decoration: underline;">free</em> to those applicants meeting the following criteria:
            </p>
            <p>
