            <p></p>
            <li><em>Must be permanent or semi permanent in a wheelchair or bed</em></li>
            <p></p>
            <li><em>Must suffer from a neurological disease such as Multiple Sclerosis or similar highly debilitating disease or have a terminal illness</em></li>
