            <p>This is a one time only offer and targeted at people who are very ill with low quality of life and probably on a lot of meds and suffering from depression.</p>

            <h3 style="color:#538b01;">Conditions of Acceptance</h3>

            <p>Applicants must agree to provide feedback on whether the cannabis had a negative or positive effect on their condition and details of that effect. They must agree to having their details recorded with the results for research only purposes. In any public forums applicants will be labelled anonymously.</p>

            <p><em style="color:#d74201; text-decoration: underline;">That is the only condition of acceptance.</em> No payment of any description is required and applicants are under no pressure of any sort to give positive results.</p>

            <p>The amount of cannabis to be supplied has not yet been determined and will depend on the number of applicants meeting the required criteria... if there are any applicants at all!</p>

            

            <h3 style="color:#538b01;">Known side effects</h3>

            <p><ul>

            <li>These particular strains can cause a feeling of paranoia and edginess that many people dislike so applicants need to be aware of this</li>
            <p></p>
            <li>The stronger strains are rough on the throat and lungs and will make people cough a lot so this trial is not recommended for anybody with lung or chest conditions</li>
            <p></p>
