            <li>Slight peripheral visual hallucinations can occur with some users as well as a greatly distorted perception of time and enhanced brightness of colours. Senses can become more acute and creative tendencies can come in waves. None of this is anything to worry about and will pass.</li>

            </ul>

            </p> 

